Localization.Name: Field Medic Kit
Localization.Description: Medical emergencies can happen any time, any place. Be prepared with this Field Medic Kit from Curelife which provides convenient and portable storage for a ParaMed Medical Device, Pancea MedGel refills, and additional medicine injectors.

Localization.Name: ParaMed Medical Device
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: CureLife
Item Type: Medical Device

The ParaMed from CureLife is a professional-grade emergency medical device designed to stabilize patients suffering from possible life-threatening injuries. Offering extremely accurate diagnostics and dosing, the ParaMed can treat more patients and offer longer relief with less risk of overdose.

Localization.Name: MedPen (Hemozal)
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: CureLife
Item Type: Medical Consumable

From the Empire’s most trusted medical company, the CureLife MedPen can rapidly dispense doses of the coagulant Hemozal during emergency situations to help relieve bleeding and improve a patient’s overall vitals. Use only as recommended.
